{"type":"message","id":"c859cd47","parentId":"c11536f7","timestamp":"2026-03-22T23:45:40.486Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户问的是官方文档是否提到 Agent Loop 采用 ReAct 算法。我需要回顾一下刚才获取的官方文档内容，看看是否有明确提到 ReAct (Reason + Act) 算法。\n\n从我刚才获取的文档来看：\n1. Agent Loop 文档 (agent-loop.md) - 描述了完整的 Agent 运行流程：intake → context assembly → model inference → tool execution → streaming replies → persistence\n2. 但没有明确提到 \"ReAct\" 这个术语\n\n让我搜索一下官方文档中是否有 ReAct 相关的提及。我可以搜索一下或者查看 Agent Runtime 相关文档。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"让我搜索一下官方文档中关于 ReAct 算法的明确提及：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_7a3de671696741c2b41713bb","name":"web_search","arguments":{"count":5,"query":"site:docs.openclaw.ai ReAct react agent loop reasoning action"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_6f3b90347f664269b2475944","name":"web_fetch","arguments":{"extractMode":"markdown","maxChars":15000,"url":"https://docs.openclaw.ai/concepts/agent.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":42608,"output":260,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":10606,"totalTokens":53474,"cost":{"input":0.00468688,"output":0.00007280000000000001,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00475968}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774223126182}}
