{"type":"message","id":"18ef32bd","parentId":"378228f6","timestamp":"2026-03-23T01:49:36.449Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户问记忆存哪里了。根据之前阅读的 Memory 文档，记忆存储在：\n1. `memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md` - 日常日志\n2. `MEMORY.md` - 长期记忆\n\n这些文件位于工作空间目录下，对于当前 Agent (fox-openclaw_ai) 是 `~/.openclaw/workspace-fox-openclaw_ai/`\n\n让我告诉用户记忆存储位置，并建议他查看或创建这些文件。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"好问题！让我告诉你 OpenClaw 记忆的存储位置：\n\n---\n\n# 记忆存储位置\n\n## 默认位置\n\n对于当前 Agent (`fox-openclaw_ai`)：\n\n```\n工作空间：~/.openclaw/workspace-fox-openclaw_ai/\n├── MEMORY.md                  # 长期记忆（可选）\n└── memory/\n    ├── 2026-03-22.md          # 昨天的日志\n    ├── 2026-03-23.md          # 今天的日志\n    └── 2026-03-24.md          # 未来的日志...\n```\n\n---\n\n## 让我检查一下你的工作空间\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_8975843c395945558da7ec07","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls -la ~/.openclaw/workspace-fox-openclaw_ai/ | grep -E \"MEMORY|memory\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":6,"output":300,"cacheRead":172153,"cacheWrite":1486,"totalTokens":173945,"cost":{"input":6.6e-7,"output":0.00008400000000000001,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00008466}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774230542787}}
