{"type":"message","id":"8d4e7d22","parentId":"6bc0ab71","timestamp":"2026-03-23T03:38:27.592Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户问的是 ACP Agents 是什么。这是 OpenClaw 中的一个概念，我之前在系统提示中看到过相关提及（runtime=\"acp\"），但需要更详细的官方文档来准确解释。让我搜索或获取相关文档。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"好的！让我查询一下 ACP Agents 的官方文档：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_4accaeb0ea7740a3a986db1b","name":"web_search","arguments":{"count":5,"query":"OpenClaw ACP Agents site:docs.openclaw.ai"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":6,"output":116,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":79060,"totalTokens":79182,"cost":{"input":6.6e-7,"output":0.00003248,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00003314}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774237088468}}
